305
00:22:47,040 --> 00:22:48,280
Tak guna.

306
00:22:49,000 --> 00:22:51,240
Cukup! Diam!

307
00:22:51,640 --> 00:22:55,080
Cukup! Berhenti!

308
00:22:55,520 --> 00:22:57,120
Saya tak tahu

309
00:22:57,440 --> 00:22:59,400
