332
00:24:49,640 --> 00:24:51,280
Saya janji saya akan tangkap
lelaki tak guna itu.

333
00:24:59,560 --> 00:25:00,600
Do Yu Gon!

334
00:25:01,440 --> 00:25:02,480
Tak guna.

335
00:25:02,560 --> 00:25:03,520
Do Yu Gon!

336
00:25:07,560 --> 00:25:08,560
Do Yu Gon!

