339
00:25:24,040 --> 00:25:25,080
Tunjuklah.

340
00:25:28,280 --> 00:25:29,360
Tak guna.

341
00:25:38,880 --> 00:25:40,880
Apa? Saya tak percaya awak terus dipukul.

