00:29:59,760 --> 00:30:01,160
Lelaki tak guna itu.

396
00:30:01,240 --> 00:30:03,280
Do Yu Gon memang lelaki yang jahat.

397
00:30:03,400 --> 00:30:06,080
Adik saya yang tangkap
lelaki tak guna itu.

398
00:30:06,160 --> 00:30:08,560
- Apa?
- Dia tak sekacak saya,

399
00:30:08,640 --> 00:30:10,040
tapi dia… Aduhai.

400
00:30:09,840 --> 00:30:11,840
[Piza Yeol Yeol]

401
00:30:10,480 --> 00:30:12,040
Pergi basuh pinggan.

402
00:30:12,120 --> 00:30:13,680
Mak perlu ke kedai sekarang.

403
00:30:14,040 --> 00:30:15,400
Baiklah. Aduhai.

404
00:30:15,800 --> 00:30:18,480
[Kita akan terus fokus]

405
00:30:18,560 --> 00:30:20,840
[untuk mengurangkan jenayah berat.]

406
00:30:21,240 --> 00:30:24,400
[- Saya hanya menjalankan tugas.]
