452
00:33:33,480 --> 00:33:35,640
- Nampak sedap. Kamu pernah rasa?
- Ia daging lembu premium.

453
00:33:35,840 --> 00:33:38,400
- Ini daging lembu berkualiti tinggi.
- Boleh beri saya sepotong?

454
00:33:42,680 --> 00:33:44,160
- Duduklah semula.
- Nah, In Seon.

455
00:34:02,040 --> 00:34:03,120
Helo.

456
00:34:03,680 --> 00:34:06,240
Awak patut berhenti merokok demi In Seon.

